PrecisSetting apart of land in Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, for the use and benefit of the FLYING DUST FIRST NATION BAND, as follows: (a) 0.040 hectares as an addition to Flying Dust First Nation Indian Reserve No. 105, and (b) another 160 hectares as an addition to its Reserve No. 105D.
